== Suggested Roles==
Thanks to its slow speed, the Sturgeon is outclassed by the [[Drake|Split Drake]] in most respects, despite its larger cargo bay, except for tasks that do not require speed to outrun other freighters. This makes the Sturgeon excellent for CLS work among your own factories, or as a fleet resupply ship, thanks to its ability to carry 16,500 cargo units.

